      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "This release constitutes a rewrite of most of the core logic in the plugin. A handful of bugs were fixed along the way as well, including:\r\n\r\n- #64 \r\n- #77 \r\n- #78\r\n- #239 \r\n- #296\r\n\r\nThis release also removes two features which were added early in the plugin's development that were difficult to maintain and did not provide much value with the direction the plugin is moving in:\r\n- Recursive search through folders\r\n- Upgrading notes to events\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* fixed #227 by @davish in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/240\r\n* Add persistent cache for events by @davish in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/204\r\n* Mobile Initial View doesn't save by @igelbox in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/285\r\n* fix displaying sidebar leaf adter restart by @igelbox in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/286\r\n* Integrate EventCache with FullCalendar view layer by @davish in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/303\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @igelbox made their first contribution in https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/pull/285\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/davish/obsidian-full-calendar/compare/0.9.5...0.10.0",
